=head1 INSTALLATION

These are the installation instructions for File::MimeInfo::SharedMimeInfoXML.

The module releases are hosted on CPAN. The module
can be installed:

=over

=item latest release from CPAN

  cpan File::MimeInfo::SharedMimeInfoXML

or

  cpanm File::MimeInfo::SharedMimeInfoXML

=item directly, as the latest development files

 cpanm git://github.com/Corion/file-mimeinfo-sharedmimeinfoxml.git

=item manually cloninig the repository:

 git clone git://github.com/Corion/file-mimeinfo-sharedmimeinfoxml.git
 cd File_MimeInfo_SharedMimeInfoXML
 perl Makefile.PL
 make
 make test
 make install

=back

